{"tid":2079763,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"明報：蓮塘口岸設人臉識別取代X光行李帶 建制議會表示港人應入鄉隨俗","createTime":"2020-06-26T04:15:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T04:18:17.000Z","uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9ae67400cc1a0118a3cd19fb745edc1ed3d33d2f","tid":2079763,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T04:15:38.000Z","msg":"蓮塘香園圍口岸開通日期未敲定，兩地政府近日頻頻邀請運輸業界到口岸參觀，多名曾參觀內地蓮塘口岸人士稱，內地在蓮塘口岸內採用新行李檢查模式，以人臉識別系統取代以往的X光行李帶，針對特定人士檢查行李，但未知系統內有何人資料。有民主派立法會議員稱，外界難以知悉蓮塘口岸的人臉識別系統是否用作政治監控；有建制派議員則認為，以人臉識別取代行李檢查可加快通關，認為港人應「入鄉隨俗」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200626/s00002/1593109879643/%e8%93%ae%e5%a1%98%e5%8f%a3%e5%b2%b8%e8%a8%ad%e4%ba%ba%e8%87%89%e8%ad%98%e5%88%a5-%e5%8f%aa%e6%9f%a5%e7%89%b9%e5%ae%9a%e8%80%85%e8%a1%8c%e6%9d%8e-%e6%b0%91%e4%b8%bb%e6%b4%be-%e9%9b%a3%e7%9f%a5%e6%94%bf%e6%b2%bb%e7%9b%a3%e6%8e%a7%e5%90%a6-%e5%bb%ba%e5%88%b6-%e6%87%89%e5%85%a5%e9%84%89%e9%9a%a8%e4%bf%97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200626%2Fs00002%2F1593109879643%2F%25e8%2593%25ae%25e5%25a1%2598%25e5%258f%25a3%25e5%25b2%25b8%25e8%25a8%25ad%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e8%2587%2589%25e8%25ad%2598%25e5%2588%25a5-%25e5%258f%25aa%25e6%259f%25a5%25e7%2589%25b9%25e5%25ae%259a%25e8%2580%2585%25e8%25a1%258c%25e6%259d%258e-%25e6%25b0%2591%25e4%25b8%25bb%25e6%25b4%25be-%25e9%259b%25a3%25e7%259f%25a5%25e6%2594%25bf%25e6%25b2%25bb%25e7%259b%25a3%25e6%258e%25a7%25e5%2590%25a6-%25e5%25bb%25ba%25e5%2588%25b6-%25e6%2587%2589%25e5%2585%25a5%25e9%2584%2589%25e9%259a%25a8%25e4%25bf%2597&d=b6PV2mHT5tDC6%2Fq4CXK2SoaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=19fa9b12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200626%2Fs00002%2F1593109879643%2F%25e8%2593%25ae%25e5%25a1%2598%25e5%258f%25a3%25e5%25b2%25b8%25e8%25a8%25ad%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e8%2587%2589%25e8%25ad%2598%25e5%2588%25a5-